eption. A new preface and an appendix on vanguard biographies have been added to this paperback edition.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 12. Dez 2020) 7aLITERARY CRITICISM / European / Spanish & Portuguese.2bisacsh1 aPérez Firmat, Gustavo, eauthor.4aut4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/aut08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDUK Archive eBook-Package 1964-1999z978311071360240uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/9780822382621zCo-access DOI >> click Walter de Gruyter40uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780822382621423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/cover/covers/9780822382621.jpg  a978-3-11-071360-2  DUK Archive eBook-Package 1964-1999c1964d1999  aEBA_DUK_ALL  aEBA_DUK_EALL  aEBA_DUK_SSHALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles